title: Rajiv Gandhi Shilpi Swasthya Bima Yojana
subtitle: subtitle

data.ABOUT: The scheme comes under the National Handicrafts Development Programme under the section Ambedkar Hastshilp Vikas Yojna.
data.AIM: Rajiv Gandhi Shilpi Swasthya Bima Yojana is aimed towards providing financial aid to the      artisan community to access the best of healthcare facilities in the country.
data.ELIGIBILITY: All Craft persons( Handicraft artisans whether male or female, between the age      group of one day to 80 years are eligible to avail the scheme.
